      "review_summary": "This PR changes QMD backend config parsing so any `memory.qmd.command` containing a backslash bypasses `splitShellArgs`, and adds backend-config tests for Windows-style command paths.\n\nPR surface: Source +21, Tests +31. Total +52 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source-level reproduction is high-confidence: current main routes `memory.qmd.command` through `splitShellArgs`, whose unquoted backslash branch consumes Windows path separators before QMD spawn resolution.",
